    • Method Detail

      • read

        ResultSet read(InputStream in,
               Context context)
        Read from an InputStream and produce a ResultSet. Note that return result may stream and so the input stream be read while the ResultSet is used. See ResultSetFactory.copyResults(ResultSet) for a ResultSet that is detached from the InputStream.
        Parameters:
        in - InputStream to read from.
        context -
        Returns:
        ResultSet

      • read

        ResultSet read(Reader in,
               Context context)
        Using read(InputStream, Context) is preferred. Read from an Reader and produce a ResultSet. Note that return result may stream and so the reader be read while the ResultSet is used. See ResultSetFactory.copyResults(ResultSet) for a ResultSet that is detached from the InputStream.
        Parameters:
        in - Reader
        context -
        Returns:
        ResultSet
